    <h3 class="title"><a href="/getting-rid-lines-airport-security#comment-15100" class="active">The limit is the number of SCREENERS, not the number of stations</a></h3>    <div class="submitted">Submitted by DensityDuck (not verified) on Tue, 2014-04-01 14:09.</div>
    <div class="content"><p>I have yet to see a security checkpoint that didn't have a station standing idle.  Double the number of people running the lines and you'll double the speed.</p>
</div>
