    <div class="content"><p>I am not talking about complete screening, but much less.   The truth is, by 9:30am on 9/11/01, the hijack and fly into building plot no longer worked, even after they had taken the cockpit.   Nobody is going to get away with a hijacking, unless they have something with them to kill all the passengers and crew.    Not saying they might not smuggle that on, but it&#8217;s harder.</p>
</div>
